Tammy Hansen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tammy_Hansen 0 Tammy Hansen Grady (also known as Tammy Hanson or Tammy Grady) is an American- born recording artist, actress, photographer and former glamour model. She was born in Los Angeles, California on September 29, 1970. She has appeared in 16 music videos. At present, she is a DP, camera operator and enjoys making films of her own.
